title: (x) Paint Bull - Capone {Mark S}
content: It's Capone, but I can't tell if it's [this weight](http://web.archive.org/web/20050817015721/http:/www.fonthaus.com/products/fonts/view.cfm?CFID=703141&CFTOKEN=74864048&SKU=PN10119) or [this weight](http://web.archive.org/web/20050817015721/http:/www.fonthaus.com/products/fonts/view.cfm?CFID=703141&CFTOKEN=74864048&SKU=PN10117). Maybe a stroke was added to the lighter weight.
author: Mark Simonson
